## Add to cart action

The **Add to cart** action is available as part of the **Action List (VX)** widget

Its primary purpose is to be placed on preview cards, allowing customers to quickly add items to cart without opening the product page.

The action has two states:

- **Add to cart:** When product can be quickly added to cart without additional selections required
- **Select options:** When product cannot be added to cart before customer selects options e.g Variations

Add to cart action added to the preview card

![](data:image/png;base64,)

Note: This action is not required on listing page as theres the Add to Cart button on the actual product form available
